This Debian package provides unofficial support for pacrunner.

In order to create the Debian package from upstream sources, do the following:
 - check the intended version number from debian/changelog
 - copy the upstream tar ball to pacrunner_<version>.orig.tar.gz
 - untar the upstream tar ball
 - copy the debian/ directory to pacrunner-<version>/
 - cd to pacrunner-<version>/ directory
 - run 'dpkg-buildpackage -rfakeroot -uc -us'
